Class StationDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • StatisticsAbstract
      • StationDefinition

  • public class StationDefinition
extends StatisticsAbstract
    Class that contains information for station and all of its information, allows you to add a day to the dataset. Retrieve the stationID, name, city, latitude, and longitude.
    Version:
    10/19/2016
    Author:
    Kyle Roller
